captions.translation: [JIUTAI] Near Gojō, she said, of the "evening face."
Near Gojō, she said, of the "evening face."
In the moment the eyes turn aside, she becomes a dream.
captions.transcription: Sora meseshi ma ni yume to nari.
captions.japaneseScript: 空目せし間に夢となり。

captions.translation: as she disapperas in the shadow of the flowers.
She disappears in the shadow of the flowers.
